org.apache.axis.EngineConfiguration, org.apache.axis.WSDDEngineConfiguration
public class AeResourceProvider
extends org.apache.axis.configuration.FileProvider

This class extends the axis file provider so we can create our own deployment context, which can then be classloader aware.
